<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of service for DenArt Body Painting Studio in NYC">
	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-6">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Terms of Service</h1>

		<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
			<p class="mb-6">Last updated: February 2026</p>

			<h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
			<p>By booking a session or visiting DenArt Body Painting Studio, you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.</p>

			<h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">2. Booking & Reservations</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>All appointments require advance booking through our online system or by phone.</li>
				<li>A deposit may be required to secure your booking, which is non-refundable unless we cancel the session.</li>
				<li>Please arrive on time for your scheduled session. Late arrivals may result in shortened service or rescheduling.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">3. Cancellation & Rescheduling</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Cancellations made less than 48 hours before your appointment forfeit the deposit.</li>
				<li>Rescheduling is permitted with at least 24 hours notice, subject to availability.</li>
