			<p>We strive to accurately represent our services through photographs and descriptions. However, final results may vary based on individual skin type, body shape, and other factors. Custom artwork is created specifically for you and may differ from stock images.</p>

			<h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">5. Model Releases & Photography</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>By default, we may use photos of your session for our portfolio and marketing unless you request otherwise.</li>
				<li>If you wish to keep your images private, please inform us before your session.</li>
				<li>You may request a model release form to grant or restrict usage rights.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">6. Health & Safety</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>All body paints we use are FDA-compliant and safe for skin contact.</li>
				<li>Please inform us of any skin conditions, allergies, or sensitivities before your session.</li>
				<li>We maintain strict hygiene standards and use disposable materials where appropriate.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">7. Payment & Pricing</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Payment is due at the time of service unless other arrangements are made.</li>
				<li>Pricing is quoted at the time of booking and may vary based on complexity, duration, and location.</li>
				<li>We accept major credit cards and digital payment methods.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
			<p>DenArt Body Painting Studio is not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from our services. Our liability is limited to the amount paid for the specific service rendered.</p>

			<h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">9. Intellectual Property</h2>
			<p>Original artwork designs created by DenArt remain the intellectual property of the studio unless a separate agreement is made. Clients receive a license to use their commissioned artwork for personal purposes.</p>

			<h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">10. Changes to Terms</h2>
			<p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Updated terms will be posted on this page and take effect upon posting.</p>

			<h2 style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Contact Us</h2>
			<p>If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Email: hello@denartny.com</li>
